<i>N'</i>

49:59.296 --> 50:01.276
<i>N'</i>

50:13.711 --> 50:15.691
<i>N'</i>

50:24.655 --> 50:26.828
Junior.

50:26.957 --> 50:28.903
Junior, you're home?

50:33.631 --> 50:35.838
Listen, son, we understand
that you need space.

50:35.966 --> 50:39.573
But you need to let us know
before you leave this house.

50:39.703 --> 50:42.081
Especially today-- you knew
we were going to church.

50:42.206 --> 50:43.082
THERESA:
We got your note, baby,

50:43.207 --> 50:44.481
but, I mean, come on, you still

50:44.575 --> 50:45.986
need permission before
you just leave the house.

50:46.076 --> 50:47.987
You don't leave us a note.

50:48.078 --> 50:49.421
Why do you care?

50:50.548 --> 50:51.583
Whafd you say?

50:51.715 --> 50:52.921
Do you even miss him, Dad?

50:53.050 --> 50:54.586
Have you even visited him?

50:54.718 --> 50:56.356
Don't you want to tell Eric
you're sorry for not

50:56.487 --> 50:57.557
being there that day
to pick him up

50:57.688 --> 50:58.598
-like you promised?
- Hey, hey!

50:58.722 --> 51:00.030
That is enough.

51:00.157 --> 51:02.103
Get in your room.

51:08.265 --> 51:09.744
I do miss him.

51:14.838 --> 51:17.011
I know you do.

51:27.685 --> 51:29.687
Hi. Uh, may I speak

51:29.787 --> 51:32.961
with your
school counselor, please?

51:33.090 --> 51:35.070
(indistinct conversations)

51:46.804 --> 51:48.784
<i>N'</i>

52:00.417 --> 52:02.419
H 9Y-

