What is this?

52:04.555 --> 52:07.434
Juniofs school counselor
has arranged for me

52:07.558 --> 52:11.267
to speak to some
students tomorrow about...

52:11.395 --> 52:12.499
texting while driving,

52:12.630 --> 52:13.973
and being an organ donor.

52:14.098 --> 52:16.078
No, no,
you're not doing that.

52:17.468 --> 52:21.143
Uh, with all due respect...

52:21.271 --> 52:23.148
what?

52:23.273 --> 52:24.911
I mean, I'm sorry,
but that's-that's not fair.

52:25.009 --> 52:26.647
Fain'!

52:26.777 --> 52:29.485
Is it fair a teenager texting
on her phone killed Eric?

52:29.613 --> 52:31.286
Is that fair?
Is it fair

52:31.415 --> 52:33.622
that we live our entire life
the way God asks,

52:33.751 --> 52:36.664
and somehow
He still finds it fit

52:36.787 --> 52:39.131
to take Eric from us?
Is that fair?

52:39.256 --> 52:41.167
- Is that fair, Theresa?
- I don't-l don't know.

52:41.291 --> 52:44.170
So you tell me
how is running down there

52:44.294 --> 52:46.296
and telling these kids
about Eric's death

52:46.430 --> 52:48.774
and how, somehow, it's part
of God's plan-- what are they

52:48.866 --> 52:50.539
-supposed to learn from that?
- I'm not gonna tell them...

52:50.668 --> 52:52.113
What are they supposed

52:52.202 --> 52:54.341
-to learn from that'?
- I don't know, David!

52:58.542 --> 53:00.146
I don't know if they're gonna
learn anything

53:00.277 --> 53:04.054
from what I have to say
tomorrow. I don't know.

53:06.016 --> 53:08.724
I know this:

53:08.852 --> 53:11.492
I'm going down there tomorrow.

53:11.622 --> 53:15.001
And if I reach one student,

53:15.125 --> 53:17.036
then maybe

53:17.161 --> 53:19.402
they will reach
another one.

53:19.530 --> 53:21.476
And then, from there,
another one.

53:22.866 --> 53:26.040
I know that my son's death

53:26.170 --> 53:27.740
has to have a purpose.

53:47.224 --> 53:49.204
(crying)

53:59.770 --> 54:01.750
<i>N'</i>

54:07.077 --> 54:09.182
THERESA:
<i>11</i> teens

54:09.279 --> 54:11.623
die every day

54:11.749 --> 54:15.595
as a result of texting
while driving.

54:15.719 --> 54:18.893
And 21% of teen drivers

54:19.022 --> 54:20.626
involved in fatal accidents

54:20.758 --> 54:23.796
were distracted
by their cell phones.

54:23.927 --> 54:27.465
Last month...

54:27.598 --> 54:30.477
my son was killed.

54:30.601 --> 54:34.276
He was hit by a car,
and the driver...

54:34.404 --> 54:37.544
was texting and driving.
A teenager.

54:37.641 --> 54:41.145
I need for you to promise

54:41.278 --> 54:44.316
that you will never
text and drive.

54:45.816 --> 54:47.659
I'm asking you to wait
until it's safe

54:47.785 --> 54:49.560
to use your cell phones.

54:49.653 --> 54:53.430
I'm pleading with you
to take...

54:53.557 --> 54:56.299
this pledge.

54:56.426 --> 54:59.270
The "no texting
while driving" pledge.

54:59.396 --> 55:01.467
You can challenge
your friends on social media

55:01.598 --> 55:03.669
to do it.

55:03.801 --> 55:05.781
And...

55:08.906 --> 55:10.852
...think about this-- about

55:10.974 --> 55:13.284
being an organ donor.

55:13.410 --> 55:15.253
Each one of you
in this very room

55:15.345 --> 55:18.417
can save up to eight people.

55:19.850 --> 55:21.989
So...

55:22.119 --> 55:24.258
if you are interested

55:24.354 --> 55:25.856
in any of that,
if you are interested

55:25.989 --> 55:27.195
in signing up.

55:27.324 --> 55:29.133
Would you raise your hands?

55:36.767 --> 55:38.713
Thank you.

55:41.872 --> 55:43.852
Looks like we're off
to a great start.

55:48.378 --> 55:49.789
<i>CECE“;
David, we have</i>

55:49.880 --> 55:51.359
got to find
a new contractor.

55:53.283 --> 55:56.059
Man, the first interest payment
on this loan is due soon

55:56.186 --> 55:59.065
and we have not even
driven the first nail yet.

55:59.189 --> 56:00.668
I know.

56:00.791 --> 56:02.134
I don't know
what to do, Cecil.

56:02.226 --> 56:04.706
I mean,
every contractor's booked.

56:04.828 --> 56:06.808
Well, not every one.

56:08.899 --> 56:10.810
No. I am not

